# Heavy upstream content (~7 MB of images, reference data, scoring code).
# Populate this directory from the upstream repo per the parent README:
#   ../README.md → "Populating bundle/"
# Source: https://github.com/fnachalearn/style-trans-fair
#
# Ignore everything in this directory EXCEPT this .gitignore itself,
# which serves the dual purpose of (a) listing the ignore rules and
# (b) keeping the directory alive in git so the path exists before
# the user runs the populate step.
*
!.gitignore
